<title>[COLOR gray][B]RECENTE Dracula A Historia Nunca Contada 2014 DUBLADO[/B]-[COLOR blue][B]XPLAYTV[/B][/COLOR]</title>
<thumbnail>https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/cCq6nnwIki2HGg6DjjtFSxxgCUY.jpg</thumbnail>
